6dad7","tid":635982,"uid":151926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"西遊記係佛祖寫既<br />\n佢將西遊記擺入堆佛經裡面等唐三藏去取<br />\n然後佛祖就按照西遊記入面既情節去比考驗唐三藏佢地<br />\n唐三藏成功取得西經後發現入面有本西遊記<br />\n發現自己所受既九九八十一難竟然同西遊記記述既係一樣<br />\n之後就叫吳承恩手抄左本西遊記黎流傳後世<br />\n而呢個手抄本就係我地今日睇到既西遊記"},{"pid":"29b363686faab4871790eb8aad55d21b6e63e4ab","tid":635982,"uid":52576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"b21bedb550457aff27e19c815e1daf774e854311","tid":635982,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecbc825abde84c5ec2ebe8b2e83fac96c0a337ef","tid":635982,"uid":40718,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9cdcb24f1837c523d3fdcbe2eff23dcf8723b5e0","tid":635982,"uid":167330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"你up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  西遊記唔係小說咩？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"佛經係故事 西遊記又係故事 點解西遊記唔係佛經？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"你收收皮先"}]}